ubuntu-kylin-software-center (0.2.1-0ubuntu1) trusty; urgency=low

  * Implement the main page with new dsigned pics.
  * build up basic UI of category and application list.
  * implement package install/uninstall/upgrade by backend thread pool .
  * use gksu to access privilege to install package.
  * Implement the dbus service to install/uninstall/upgrade packages.
  * Rewrite the data management by object abstract.
  * Get reviews information from those of ubuntu.
  * Add screenshot and review/rating procedure.
  * Implement the remote data with multiprocessing.
  * Add task view of package management procedure
  * Implement basic ui with new dsigned ui pics 
  * rewrite the dbus service with thread daemon.
  * optimize the interfaces between frontend and backend
  * Add search widget for package search. 
  * Implement search method with xapian.
  * Implement detail view of application.
  * Add wait spin ui.
  * Add screenshots and reviews show.
  * Optimize the backend data management.
  * Fix many little problems.
  * Rebuid the start process to solve some operation conflicts.
  * Remove print log operations and implement with logging.
  * Modify the default cache and resource path.

 -- Shine Huang (shine) <shenghuang@ubuntukylin.com>  Tue, 11 Mar 2014 17:23:11 +0800

